	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was reading not to long ago that 20 stamina (as used in character creation which I imagine holds true throughout the game as well) at level 60 yields 80hp.&nbsp;&nbsp;That being said (currently level 34) 20 additional stamina will probably give me about 40 hits points or so (if what I read was correct).  This item doesnt have stamina as a stat but it does have 20 hitpoints which would be about the equivalent of 40 stamina for my level.  Any truth to that?  If so it makes the item just that much more attractive in my mind.  I'm wearing a Spider Fur belt right now but will be attempting to get this belt in the next few days.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
