re more than 2 could aggro me, only pausing to get my drum.  Now I have 11% more haste, and I'll try getting to the assassin in guk again : ) (already got the mask, really going for the bag)<br>&nbsp;<br>Dont make me drive by punch ye druid!<br>Longtounge Speedmyster<br>52 Bard of Xegony<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=347604" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=347604</a></td></tr>
