	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.36]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Grimlings had the owlbear caves on Veeshan last night.&nbsp;&nbsp;This spawn is in the far left hand room in the owlbear caves.  It's ph is a grimling guard at the back of the room.  Next to him is a Grimling manacrafter.  Both of them are exactly 10 minute spawns.  I killed the manacrafter first and then the guard.  This gave me a heads up each time the guard/Gleeknot was gonna spawn.  <br><br>I camped it for 2-3 hours.  Usually it alternated between Gleeknot and ph, but at least once there were 3 ph's in a row.  He dropped the hat 3x before dropping the belt.<br><br>I am a 46 pally and everything in the room was green except Gleeknot who was light blue.  However, he hits hard and fast and routinely took me to around 2 bubbles of health.  The greenies did not aggro unless I got very close to them and I never had any adds when fighting Gleeknot.<br><br>During the down time, you can take out quite a few of the green mobs and collect runes, weapons and the rare gems for sale later.<br><br>Good Luck<br>&nbsp;<br>Fenadin, Yazook and Fastolph of the Veeshan Server</td></tr>
